Those who keep one foot firmly planted in the past and one far in the future are prone to defecate on the present.<br><br>
Visit the past without seeking answers to a test that you have already failed...Don't try to change the question so that the wrong answer will fit.  Life has instructed you... you know the correct answers.<br><br>
Visit the future without fear that you won't know the answers.  Fear will cloud that wisdom that you already have!<br><br>
